HEADWORD: Unguard
<hw>Un*guard"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>guard</ets>.]</ety> <def>To deprive of a guard; to
